I had one more, which
doesn't have anything

00:52:49.610 --> 00:52:51.350
to do with the book itself.

00:52:51.350 --> 00:52:53.870
Obviously, both of you
teach at the business school

00:52:53.870 --> 00:52:55.290
at Standford.

00:52:55.290 --> 00:52:57.800
And many Googlers are
